    @{b}o@{ub} Popping up MUI-Prefs from the PopUp-gadget in the window-
      border might fail for some, if the pointer is right above the
      Textfield.gadget. If MUI-Prefs won't pop up, try again, and see
      to it that you don't have the pointer above the textfield.gadget.
      This is obviously not a fault of Misc, but of MUI.
